#. <section class="sutta" id="sn55.31"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn55.31:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 55"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 55"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn55.31:0.2"
msgid "4. Puññābhisandavagga"
msgstr "4. Overflowing Merit"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 31. Paṭhamapuññābhisandasutta → abhisandasuttaṃ (bj) | abhisanda 1 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn55.31:0.3"
msgid "31. Paṭhamapuññābhisandasutta"
msgstr "31. Overflowing Merit (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.391"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.31:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn55.31:1.2"
msgid "“Cattārome, bhikkhave, puññābhisandā kusalābhisandā sukhassāhārā."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, there are these four kinds of overflowing merit, overflowing "
"goodness that nurture happiness."

msgctxt "sn55.31:1.3"
msgid "Katame cattāro?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn55.31:1.4"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako buddhe aveccappasādena samannāgato hoti—"
msgstr "Firstly, a noble disciple has experiential confidence in the Buddha …"

msgctxt "sn55.31:1.5"
msgid "itipi so bhagavā … pe … satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn55.31:1.6"
msgid "Ayaṃ paṭhamo puññābhisando kusalābhisando sukhassāhāro."
msgstr ""
"This is the first kind of overflowing merit, overflowing goodness that "
"nurtures happiness."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.31:2.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako dhamme aveccappasādena samannāgato hoti—"
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, a noble disciple has experiential confidence in the teaching …"

msgctxt "sn55.31:2.2"
msgid "svākkhāto bhagavatā dhammo … pe … paccattaṃ veditabbo viññūhīti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn55.31:2.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ dutiyo puññābhisando kusalābhisando sukhassāhāro."
msgstr ""
"This is the second kind of overflowing merit, overflowing goodness that "
"nurtures happiness."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.31:3.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako saṅghe aveccappasādena samannāgato hoti—"
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, a noble disciple has experiential confidence in the Saṅgha …"

msgctxt "sn55.31:3.2"
msgid ""
"suppaṭipanno bhagavato sāvakasaṅgho … pe … anuttaraṃ puññakkhettaṃ lokassāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn55.31:3.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ tatiyo puññābhisando kusalābhisando sukhassāhāro."
msgstr ""
"This is the third kind of overflowing merit, overflowing goodness that "
"nurtures happiness."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.31:4.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako ariyakantehi sīlehi samannāgato hoti "
"akhaṇḍehi … pe … samādhisaṃvattanikehi."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, a noble disciple’s ethical conduct is loved by the noble ones, "
"unbroken, unflawed, unblemished, untainted, liberating, praised by sensible "
"people, not mistaken, and leading to immersion."

msgctxt "sn55.31:4.2"
msgid "Ayaṃ catuttho puññābhisando kusalābhisando sukhassāhāro."
msgstr ""
"This is the fourth kind of overflowing merit, overflowing goodness that "
"nurtures happiness."

msgctxt "sn55.31:4.3"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro puññābhisandā kusalābhisandā sukhassāhārā”ti."
msgstr ""
"These are the four kinds of overflowing merit, overflowing goodness that "
"nurture happiness.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn55.31:4.4"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
